snippet.title: RevolutionVoid
snippet.description: Revolution Void is the electronic jazz music project of producer Jonah Dempcy. The music of Revolution Void ranges from upbeat dancefloor-friendly breaks to dark and moody downtempo soundscapes, from mainstream sensibilities to avant-garde experimentalism.
